      | top  | Datasource Updated |
      | body | 1 match added      |
    When Operator search the created address datasource:
      | province  | {KEY_SORT_CREATED_ADDRESS.province} |
      | kota      | {KEY_SORT_CREATED_ADDRESS.city}     |
      | kecamatan | {KEY_SORT_CREATED_ADDRESS.district} |
